        <item>
            <title>Casio 经典跳字表发表 50 年，推 Casiotron 限量版全球仅 4,000 枚</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/02/21/casio-casiotron-trn50-2a-limited-edition/life-tech/watch-wireless-home/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=casio-casiotron-trn50-2a-limited-edition</link>
